---
title: Tex-Mex Cheesy Beef Burger with Charred Corn Aioli & Potato Wedges
description: There's a secret X-factor in these burgers: Tex-Mex flavours! The spice blend in the beef patties and the charred corn aioli take them to next-level tastiness. Add some potato wedges and this might just be your new favourite dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-cheesy-beef-burger-82b886fb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/tex-mex-cheesy-beef-burger-5dc3530a8c2c8f418b272219-bf28c139.pdf
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
